{"tid":2408993,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"馬狗指Dogecoin太集中 籲持倉者沽貨","createTime":"2021-02-15T12:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T13:01:18.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3a2ba2daf00b46f861a5120013628ee803c03081","tid":2408993,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"馬斯克指狗狗幣太集中 籲持倉者沽貨<br />\n日期：2021年2月15日 下午7:33<br />\n電動車廠商特斯拉(Tesla)創辦人馬斯克(Elon Musk)近期不斷唱好加密貨幣，他最新在Twitter發推文，指個人認為狗狗幣(Dogecoin)的唯一真正問題是太集中，全力支持狗狗幣的主要持有者出售他們大部分持倉。<br />\n<br />\n狗狗幣價格波動，根據Coindesk報價，狗狗幣最新跌16.74%，報0.055美元，24小時高見0.066美元，低位報0.048美元。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉早前披露公司購入約值15億美元(約117億港元)的比特幣，佔Tesla於去年底時手頭現金的8％，並預告將於短期內接受以比特幣，作為購買電動車的一種付款方式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd99f95f0509fccbd148474855867c0ca6af648","tid":2408993,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"推高完又推跌"},{"pid":"5790bb1da67dcb38381e1f2a1e519be2fa082ca8","tid":2408993,"uid":221856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"其實真係咁解讀?<br />\n<br />\nif major Dogecoin holders sell most of their coins, it will get my full support. Too much concentration is the only real issue imo.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Major DOGE holders&quot;"},{"pid":"12c0d0d9d1e08f20161c4c9850fd0216422c5567","tid":2408993,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:22:11.000Z","msg":"老千😂<br />\n昆傻仔<br />\n根本btc先至係真命天子"},{"pid":"4e05bdc043cccc27b275159a92e2cbcd70b37040","tid":2408993,"uid":311611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:22:25.000Z","msg":"跟本個思想係人人都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大家先會用來交易<br />\n<br />\n炒乜9？"},{"pid":"a8bc47f4bf668f3d9d95fa239c64e9ccb6f21d34","tid":2408993,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5790bb1da67dcb38381e1f2a1e519be2fa082ca8"